page.title: 07JOBS OF DATCHET COMMUTERS
page.content: by Kelly,Gemma,Simone,Lucy On Tuesday 9th July,27 Datchet to London commuters told us about their jobs.Here is the range of job titles:- {TRAINEE TRADING STANDARDS OFFICER {CLERK IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUSTICE {ADMINISTRATIVE CLERK IN SECURITY FIRM {INTERNATIONAL SOFTWARE CONSULTANT {COMPUTER SYSTEMS ANALYST (2) {ELECTRONIC ENGINEERING SUPERVISOR {CHARTERED CIVIL ENGINEER {OIL REFINING ENGINEER {CHARTERED PATENT AGENT {INTERNATIONAL INSURANCE {PERSONNEL ADVISER {CIVIL SERVANT(2) {OIL COMPANY EXECUTIVE ARCHITECT {BANKING(2) ACCOUNTANT {ADMINISTRATOR SOLICITOR {MANAGERIAL(3) MARKETING EXECUTIVE {BARRISTER INTERIOR DESIGNER {
